TAGALOG

Pang-abay

* Ito ay mga salitang umuuri sa isang pang-uri o pandiwa.
* Ipinapakilala nito ang kanilang paraan, panahon, pinangyarihan, at katiyakan.

Halimbawa:
Bakit ka lumalakad nang mabagal?

(Sinasagot ng "mabagal" kung paano lumalakad ang taong tinatanong.)



(Balarila, p. 402-403)
*******************************************************
ENGLISH

Adverbs

* These are words and phrases that describe an adjective or verb.
* They answer "in what way," "when," "where," and "how certain."

Halimbawa:
Bakit ka lumalakad nang mabagal?

("Mabagal" or slowly answers how the person was walking or "lumalakad.") 
